Blueface is dedicated to respecting your privacy and complying with all applicable data protection and privacy laws. We are committed to safeguarding your personal data and ensuring its secure handling.
The Privacy Policy explains in detail what types of data we collect, how we use it, and the purposes behind its collection. This includes personal data, call records, and information gathered through cookies. Transparency in data practices is a key focus.
By downloading and reviewing the Privacy Policy, users gain insights into how Blueface handles their information. Understanding your data rights and how your information is managed empowers you to make informed decisions and trust in our commitment to data privacy.
